{"tid":1391161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"5/8 三罷職工盟你做緊啲咩","createTime":"2019-07-31T10:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:59:46.000Z","uid":57857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ecd7b4ddfdfc2416bcc3aa799bae82a5152a740e","tid":1391161,"uid":57857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:50:20.000Z","msg":"事源：<a href=\"https://hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/content/%E5%8A%9B%E7%88%AD%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B28%E6%9C%885%E6%97%A5%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkctu.org.hk%2Fzh-hant%2Fcontent%2F%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E5%2591%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B28%25E6%259C%25885%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=bb98dd92\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/content/%E5%8A%9B%E7%88%AD%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B28%E6%9C%885%E6%97%A5%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5</a><br />\n先唔講呢場運動你有咩貢獻<br />\n講罷工要動員咁多行業工會理論上你職工盟應該應該最多connection幫到好多手<br />\n你同我而家係度呼籲呼籲有春用?<br />\npractical啲聯絡下工會做下啲法律野黎保障罷工嘅人得唔得?<br />\n雖然大家都知政黨一向都唔係好可靠, 但係今次泛民啲議員都叫識搵自己位置<br />\n屌你職工盟班撚屌係度鳩講呼籲, 前線嘅人出街跪係地下求人響應喇你做緊乜撚野呀<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以比定啲法律基礎嘅文宣出黎等大家罷工都罷得安心(如有), 咁應該會多啲人響應<br />\n有心啲仲可以send email比晒以下註冊工會求佢地響應5/8罷工, 但係好仆街搵唔到一個list有佢地email<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/news/TU16_add_list_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fnews%2FTU16_add_list_c.pdf&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=12e68f92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/news/TU16_add_list_c.pdf</a><br />\n最低限度, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屋企有事/無啦啦病左</span></span></strong>呢啲都冇人想架係咪先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">講工會方面真係比工聯會控制左大部份, 難度唔細但係大家加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"7df3804f8003ff907587b748c594a43d4046f8bc","tid":1391161,"uid":57857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fa13969f6031d5ef21d8c86a7fb9bb02e48bfe9","tid":1391161,"uid":57857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"要法律文宣"},{"pid":"de9d16bec1223ce51db05783c28c00aab607a418","tid":1391161,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要說&quot;推&quot;, <br />\n<br />\n試著說：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Hf7ppz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Hf7ppz.png&h=37691996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkS5Vwe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxkS5Vwe.png&h=b234ed26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/TZSULu5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZSULu5.jpg&h=90f35e94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0c4faed54146d23425ca52dc7454535441659eb","tid":1391161,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:59:46.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［請廣傳]大量文宣！大量文宣！大量文宣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390733</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}